<br>
Did they think?<br>
<br>
What was their 'vision' of the Planes?  Of Sebilis?    <br>
<br>
Or has the game evolved from the players outmanuevering the programmers?  Remember when you could levitate in Sky, and avoid Island 2?<br>
<br>
